4. p

8.7 p

A. 

#  successes  7 trials  25 successes  trials 
successes <- 7
trials <- 25
pbar <- successes / trials

B. 

#  qnorm()  z
#  90%  = 1  0.90 =0.10 /2 = 0.05
z <- -qnorm(0.05)
# 
margin.of.error <- z * sqrt(pbar * (1 - pbar) / trials)

C. 

# 
conf.interval <- c(pbar - margin.of.error, pbar + margin.of.error)
conf.interval
## [1] 0.1322925 0.4277075
